PrecisAmendments to Orders in Council P.C. 1984-1430 and P.C. 1985-1824, which authorized the acquisition of certain tracts of land situated within the boundaries of the proposed Grasslands National Park, in the the Province of Saskatchewan, known as the Larsen Ranch, in order to substitute a revised description of the lands thereby intended to be acquired.
